{"article_id":"otiBnPcqHie3mPXk","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Debbie Wasserman Schultz To Step Down As Democratic Chair After Convention","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Amid furor over an email leak","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that revealed a bias against Bernie Sanders inside the Democratic National Committee ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"U.S. Rep. Debbie Wasserman Schultz announced Sunday","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"she will step down as chair .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Wasserman Schultz will still open and close the convention ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"she said in a statement ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and `` address our delegates about the stakes","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"involved in this election not only for Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"but for all Americans . '' `` We have planned a great and unified Convention this week","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"and I hope and expect","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that the DNC team","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"that has worked so hard","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"to get us to this point","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"will have the strong support of all Democrats","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"in making sure","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"this is the best convention","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"we have ever had , ''","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"the statement continued .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Donna Brazile , former Al Gore campaign manager and Bill Clinton adviser , will be the interim committee chair through the election ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"according to a verified tweet from DNC Communications Director Luis Miranda :","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"DNC Vice Chair Donna Brazile will serve as Interim Chair through the election","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"# DNCinPHL","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"- Luis Miranda","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"( @ LuisMiranda )","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"July 24 , 2016","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"In response , Sanders said","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Wasserman Schultz made `` the right decision for the future of the Democratic Party .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"President Obama ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"who appointed Wasserman Schultz in 2011 ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"praised her service ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"the Florida congresswoman 's `` leadership of the DNC has meant","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"that we had someone","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"who brought Democrats together . ''","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"In a statement , Hillary Clinton thanked her `` longtime friend '' for her leadership .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"`` There 's simply no one better","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"at taking the fight to the Republicans than Debbie . ''","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Clinton also announced","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that Wasserman Schultz will serve as honorary chair of the campaign 's `` 50-state program","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to gain ground","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"and elect Democrats in every part of the country ''","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"and that the two will campaign together","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"both to help elect Clinton to the White House","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"and to help with Wasserman Schultz 's House re-election campaign .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"Donald Trump campaign manager Paul Manafort said","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Wasserman Schultz resigned over `` her failure","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"to secure the DNC 's email servers and the rigged system","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"she set up with the Clinton campaign . ''","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Clinton should follow Wasserman Schultz 's lead","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"and drop out over her failure","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"to safeguard top-secret , classified information both on her unauthorized home server and while traveling abroad .","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"Wasserman Schultz 's emails only put the Democratic Party at risk ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"but Clinton 's emails put all of America at risk .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Earlier in the day , Wasserman Schultz was replaced as chair of the Democratic National Convention ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"which begins Monday in Philadelphia .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Ohio Rep. Marcia Fudge was named the new convention chair .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"The emails ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"which were released by WikiLeaks","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"just days before the party 's convention launches in Philadelphia ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"appear to show top DNC officials trading ideas","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"on how to hurt Sanders at the polls .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"In one email out of the 20,000","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"leaked ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"the committee 's chief financial officer , Brad Marshall , appears to float an idea","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to question the Vermont senator 's Jewish faith .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"In an interview with CNN , Sanders , once again , called on Wasserman Schultz to resign .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"`` It goes without saying","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"the function of the DNC , ''","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"Sanders said ,","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"`` is to represent all of the candidates","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"to be fair and even-minded . ''","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"Sanders also called the emails an `` outrage '' and `` sad ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"but also said","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"they do not come as `` a great shock . ''","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"He believes","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"that the DNC was `` at opposition to our campaign '' all along ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"he said Sunday morning .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"`` I mean ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"there 's no question to my mind","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"and I think","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"no question to any objective observer 's mind","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"that the DNC was supporting Hillary Clinton ,","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"and was at opposition to our campaign , ''","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"Sanders said .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"He had been saying for months","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that he believes","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Wasserman Schultz should resign .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"She should step down ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"`` not only because of the prejudice","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"[ the DNC ] showed during the campaign","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"but also because I think","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"we need new leadership","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"that will open up that party '' to working people , young people","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"and `` have the kind of vitality","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"we need . ''","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"Clinton has had a long-standing relationship with the DNC and Wasserman Schultz .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Wasserman Schultz was the co-chair of her 2008 bid for president .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Sanders is a relative newcomer to the Democratic Party and the DNC ,","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"having long served as an independent in the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Still , Sanders and others feel","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"that the DNC chair should remain neutral during a nominating process .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"On NBC 's Meet the Press , Sanders would n't say","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"whether Wasserman Schultz should be forced to resign","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"before the Democratic convention begins .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"But some of his supporters went there","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"- commentator and activist Van Jones tweeted","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that he 'll speak out","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"until she steps down :","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"She will not have a speaking role at this week 's convention ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"according to several reports .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Blowback to the emails came from all corners of the political world Sunday","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"- including Clinton supporters and Donald Trump .","depth":5},{"id":117,"text":"Former DNC Chair and Virginia Gov . Terry McAuliffe ,","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"who is a Clinton supporter ,","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"called the leak `` very disturbing ''","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"if true","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"and told NPR","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"that the chair 's job should be `` to remain neutral . ''","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"`` I sat in that chair in 2004","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"trying to navigate all the different candidates","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"we had , ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"`` But","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"if you had people in there","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"who were trashing one of the candidates ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"I can tell you this ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"if I were still chairman ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"they would n't be working there .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"I mean ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that is just totally unacceptable behavior . ''","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Clinton campaign manager Robby Mook also called the emails `` disturbing ''","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"and something","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"that `` voters need to reflect on . ''","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"Trump also blasted the emails via Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"they would make it hard for Sanders to continue supporting Clinton :","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"The Wikileaks e-mail release today was so bad to Sanders","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"that it will make it impossible for him to support her ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"unless he is a fraud !","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"July 23 , 2016","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Sorry folks ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"but Bernie Sanders is exhausted ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"just ca n't go on any longer .","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"He is trying to dismiss the new e-mails and DNC disrespect .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"SAD !","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"July 24 , 2016","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"But Sanders maintained","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"that his support for Clinton is strong ,","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"his immediate message to his supporters now is that `` disastrous '' Donald Trump must be defeated .","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"`` My second message is that we continue the political revolution . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":319,"left":0,"right":318,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":318,"left":273,"right":317,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":184,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":177,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":163,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":161,"right":162,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":175,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":164,"right":174,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":5,"right":6,"rela